SELECT auctionId FROM n6s0 UNION SELECT auctionId FROM n6s1 UNION SELECT auctionId FROM n6s2 UNION SELECT auctionId FROM n6s3 UNION SELECT auctionId FROM n6s4 UNION SELECT auctionId FROM n6s5 INTO n6_chk;
